#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn27.3"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn27.3:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 27 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 27 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn27.3:0.2"
msgid "1. Kilesavagga "
msgstr "1. Corruptions "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn27.3:0.3"
msgid "3. Viññāṇasutta "
msgstr "3. Consciousness "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli3.233, sc1
msgctxt "sn27.3:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ. "
msgstr "At Sāvatthī. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn27.3:1.2"
msgid "“Yo, bhikkhave, cakkhuviññāṇasmiṃ chandarāgo, cittasseso upakkileso. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, desire and greed for eye consciousness, "

msgctxt "sn27.3:1.3"
msgid "Yo sotaviññāṇasmiṃ … "
msgstr "ear consciousness, "

msgctxt "sn27.3:1.4"
msgid "yo ghānaviññāṇasmiṃ … "
msgstr "nose consciousness, "

msgctxt "sn27.3:1.5"
msgid "yo jivhāviññāṇasmiṃ … "
msgstr "tongue consciousness, "

msgctxt "sn27.3:1.6"
msgid "yo kāyaviññāṇasmiṃ … "
msgstr "body consciousness, "

msgctxt "sn27.3:1.7"
msgid "yo manoviññāṇasmiṃ chandarāgo, cittasseso upakkileso. "
msgstr "or mind consciousness is a corruption of the mind. "

msgctxt "sn27.3:1.8"
msgid "Yato kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhuno imesu chasu ṭhānesu cetaso upakkileso pahīno hoti, nekkhammaninnañcassa cittaṃ hoti. "
msgstr "When a mendicant has given up mental corruption in these six cases, their mind inclines to renunciation. "

msgctxt "sn27.3:1.9"
msgid "Nekkhammaparibhāvitaṃ cittaṃ kammaniyaṃ khāyati, abhiññā sacchikaraṇīyesu dhammesū”ti. "
msgstr "A mind imbued with renunciation is declared to be capable of directly knowing anything that can be realized.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn27.3:1.10"
msgid "Tatiyaṃ. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
